  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505131005\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcE0HoCcMhjUKYPbiacF7Oiagaia5PkA9BA4iajMtmldVlE45CH36jKjPpQiaA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d9d0d367&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcE0HoCcMhjUKYPbiacF7Oiagaia5PkA9BA4iajMtmldVlE45CH36jKjPpQiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：peter东 英智</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">想知道全球各大企业对大模型是如何使用的大模型的，今年和去年有哪些不同，请看Artificial Analysis发布的2025年第一季度AI应用报告，把握AI发展的潮流趋势。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2025年上半年，大模型正在从技术边界走向生产现实。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">横跨欧美亚上千家企业的最新调研揭示，生成式AI已不再只是研发试验品，45%的企业已将其部署到生产环境中。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">工程研发、客户支持和营销成为AI最活跃的前线！</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这份来自一千多人的汇总报告，既包括大型科技公司，也包括橱窗企业，政府及教育部门。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过这份报告，能全面了解当前大模型在各行各业的使用情况。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130993\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5390920554854981\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1586\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1586\" data-height=\"855\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"303\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b40e9b1e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcEZmibtmycZRUkpmQRboxdpjg51qc2hJUtm0nrKh7zGhUTFFJ6YYVcolg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">报告回答的第一个问题，是大模型究竟如何被使用的，结果显示，用于生产的大模型只占45%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">23%的受访者将大模型用于原型构建，27%将大模型用于搜索信息。看起来大模型正在进入生成端，还任重道远。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130991\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8987854251012146\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"741\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"741\" data-height=\"666\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"505\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=08731188&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcE8xzJwDDgRtNE5ACLjLbENRA6GuLYEles5Eic4qps2K4YRuGBwNQsk8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8bc421a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">用户如何为AI付费</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">至于人们如何为AI付费，32%的受访者会构建定制化的大模型，27%只是通过api购买标准的大模型服务，而25%的受访者既要又要，而16%的受访者是白嫖党。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130992\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8621997471554994\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"791\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"791\" data-height=\"682\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"485\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=02e4e4c9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcE1guSbm9wZfIMzicibictmCJDKRWnGpdsKzDqDtbkSERa8UVxu5OR8X6dg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在对未来的12个月的AI使用的预期，大部分受访者（66%）希望AI能被用于工程及研发中，其次是用于客户支持（37%）及销售（33%）中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">前者对应的是可解释性及鲁棒性的增强，后者则是预期大模型未来会情商更高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130994\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4453125\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"684\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"250\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=25a689f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcEmObYMHoA5jqySAFXtDFDRUgTKLvibEibS9OWvIImKEiavLlMKbVpM3NvQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">至于有哪些因素是当前使用大模型遇到的挑战时，受访者提到最多（55%）的大模型的知识水平不足。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一半的受访者则担心大模型时不时化身人工智障，同时半数受访者指出高昂的成本是使用大模型的一大挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">除此之外，大模型和其它设备的整合，以及响应速度，监管合规等也是受访者认为当前应用大模型时面对的挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130990\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.44323284156510584\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1559\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1559\" data-height=\"691\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"249\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=15400baf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcEbK7fMQPazFaoLMbhCepYdI6RlCQOJ2mIYkmdjrVAQr93icyaZ9bJEKA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6700c77f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">激烈的红海竞争</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在最常用的大模型聊天工具上，ChapGPT的先发优势依旧，而Gemini和Claude紧随其后。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">国产的大模型则被归到了other之中，这可能是由于受访者多位于欧美印地区有关。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">值得注意的是，当前用户大多同时使用多家的大模型，受访者平均使用4.7家不同的大模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这说明市场还处在红海竞争期，大多用户不具有太强的品牌粘性，而是会货比三家。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">品牌忠诚尚未形成，用户正用脚投票。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130996\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35313531353135313\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1515\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1515\" data-height=\"535\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"198\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bcba789a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcE2KQLrbk56PCdUK0wdW8fibWPckNkgkUldBn8F0bG3Ju0ZLwMhY9x7SQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130995\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42108667529107374\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1546\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1546\" data-height=\"651\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"237\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d1b771a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcEpRvicxdib6x507A7ADuBkaaCYMy4fWaWeXzkibdUcJboGuGg8y93riaGIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比一年前的24年，OpenAI的模型保持了领先地位，谷歌的Gemini和Deepseek进步最快，claude和llama则略显颓势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同时这一年，也诞生了诸如xAI的Grok和阿里的Qwen这样的新玩家。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130997\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4335483870967742\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1550\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1550\" data-height=\"672\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"244\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a9a34267&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcENNib0IaibxapKtNCNU3vpiafDQ1KH20jZRt3ibYOxuFHDpxoOibDjvic53Gw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而在大模型编程助手这一定制化赛道上，用的最多还是Copliot和Curser，而国产的工具如Trace等则没有被统计。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130998\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4222078760490639\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1549\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1549\" data-height=\"654\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"237\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e7624050&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcEickg3gamt66QrT8HYZlbAYjJpWW6k5BCAY9SzweHibvHPybcCXQ4fedQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在全球各地受访者对中国大模型应用的接受程度上来看，大部分（55%）受访者接受中国产的大模型，但要求模型部署在中国之外，这一比例在欧美尤其高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着国产大模型的出海，需要如Manus这样借助第三国出海，方能获得欧美市场。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505130999\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4086845466155811\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1566\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1566\" data-height=\"640\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"229\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=88789c6d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcErxuTiaSfFo8icCDSytDExWQZEyF2TkJyWHAl4okqamAERwvey3ibXC8WA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6700c77f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">大模型的训练硬件</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在大模型的训练硬件上，英伟达还是占据了绝对优势地位（78%），其次用到较多的是谷歌的TPU和苏妈的AMD。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mdocc1ng30z\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505131000\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4064885496183206\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1572\" height=\"439\" style=\"width:100%;\" width=\"1074\" data-width=\"1572\" data-height=\"639\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"228\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f2ce1e5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcELQZGsGC1RPTWMW0eYhSExvTjhOw17JxHEoIRcDn5YVMicSJ3xt30CPw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">除了LLM，该报告还涉及多模态应用，例如语言生成中多应用OpenAI的模型，但其优势并不是碾压性的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">受访者多关注语音的稳定性和质量，生成的语音是否真实，延迟是否高等因素。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505131001\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4157963446475196\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1532\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1532\" data-height=\"637\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"234\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40f9919d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcEn1ZWKaSicyyRxDRVzfmYMJneYOkDy3dqaUp9gibddMY5SUEgZ4pUj97w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而在视频生成任务中，受访者使用的模型同样多来自openAI和谷歌两大巨头，使用最多的依旧是OpenAI的模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但关注点变成了对提示词的遵循程度及成本这两个因素，这反应了当前视频生成模型在听懂并遵循用户指令上任需改进。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505131002\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43139757498404596\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1567\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1567\" data-height=\"676\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"242\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=93373905&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcEgrCVGMANtoq2feWx265oEwWudbMy0BNVjvxQyiamQdicKBdIibpoGonmQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">总结这份大模型应用情况报告，2025年上半年AI应用迎来关键转折。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">45%的企业已将AI投入生产环境，工程研发（66%）、客户支持（37%）和营销（33%）成为最热门场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI守擂，谷歌Gemini强势来袭。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505131003\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"640\" data-height=\"426\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"374\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8fcbabb5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb31wsBZ0UsiaqfCOurUkHmcERibiadwq8WJGKamwRGVic8aNWpcKrYPnHKrrG41tngwPXgPJYZHricpwDQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">中国模型亦受全球企业谨慎接纳——55%的受访者愿使用，但仅限非中国基础设施。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">多模型混战成为常态，企业平均评估4.7个LLM，而NVIDIA以78%的份额统治训练硬件市场，凸显生态壁垒。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与此同时，可靠性、成本和智能水平仍是AI落地的三大「拦路虎」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://artificialanalysis.ai/downloads/ai-adoption-survey/2025/Artificial-Analysis-AI-Adoption-Survey-H1-2025.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://artificialanalysis.ai/downloads/ai-adoption-survey/2025/Artificial-Analysis-AI-Adoption-Survey-H1-2025.pdf</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "报告揭示 2025 年全球大模型应用现状，企业部署率达 45%，用户平均使用 4.7 个模型，市场竞争激烈，忠诚度低。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "报告揭示 2025 年全球大模型应用现状，企业部署率达 45%，用户平均使用 4.7 个模型，市场竞争激烈，忠诚度低。",
  "summary": "文章基于 Artificial Analysis 发布的 2025 年第一季度 AI 应用报告，深入分析了全球大模型在企业中的应用现状与趋势。报告指出，45%的企业已将大模型部署到生产环境，工程研发、客户支持和营销是主要应用领域。用户平均同时使用 4.7 家不同的大模型，表明市场处于红海竞争阶段，用户忠诚度不高。文章还探讨了用户付费模式（定制化模型与 API 服务），并指出了大模型应用面临的主要挑战，包括知识水平不足、可靠性问题和高昂成本。此外，报告还提及了 NVIDIA 在训练硬件市场的绝对优势，以及中国大模型在全球市场中面临的部署限制。报告还预测了未来 12 个月 AI 在工程研发、客户支持和销售领域的持续增长预期，并分析了 OpenAI、Google Gemini 等主要模型提供商的市场动态。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
